{
  "texts": [
    "The number on X axis corresponds to the serial number of the research dataset.",
    "As can be seen from Figure 1 that the same algorithm has different learning and modeling time on datasets with different characteristics.",
    "The overall trend shows that the modeling time of NB algorithm is the shortest on most datasets, while the modeling time of ensemble method AB is significantly several orders of magnitude higher.",
    "Dataset characteristics that affect modeling time will be further discussed and analyzed later.",
    "In view of the fact that the memory usage of the eight algorithms in learning and modeling on different datasets also presents an order of magnitude difference, this paper compares the memory occupation result values after logarithmic, as shown in Figure 2."
  ]
}